Razor Claw mingled with the crowd, he was beginning to feal comfortable with
the group.He thought about his counterpart, (Dinobot), he knew what his
capabilities were, he wondered if his donor had similar capabilities. He
wondered if they looked the same, thought the same, acted the same. Then
another thought came to him, what if they smelled the same. (Like the polar
bear recognized Ice's scent.)

(Razor Claw doesn't know that Dinobot's a transmetal)

Razor Claw stood up and aproached Rachet. "You're a pretty big bot, you must
be handy to have around." he was slowly calming down but he still didn't
like being there.
